\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]Udo... coach...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Nfufu~♪ Finally, Neon-chan, you've arrived! First of all,
let me congratulate you on reaching this room~

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Enough with the excuses... What do you intend to do?
What have you done to the three of them?
\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Three people? What are you talking about?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Don't play dumb! Kino, Sawa, and Momo, the three of
them!

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]I approached Coach Udo and grabbed him by the
collar.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Ah... I see, you're talking about the video. Come to
think of it, I did mention their names in the 4P
video, so it's no wonder you noticed (laughs).
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]...You bastard!

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Hey, Minato-chan... Are you misunderstanding
something?
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]...Huh? Misunderstanding?

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]You're treating me like the bad guy, but... let me ask
you this... did any of them show any signs of
discomfort?
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]That's... but, still, treating them so cruelly...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Even if it's measured by Minato-chan's standards...
those girls desired it, and I simply responded to
their wishes... That's all there is to it.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Besides... even if they're friends, isn't it overstepping to
meddle in their relationship with three people?
They're not children, you know?

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]......I'm at a loss for words. My anger fades away in the
face of Coach Udo's unexpected counterattack.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Well... I can't say I don't understand Minato-chan's
point of view. In society, it's considered an
impure act, and above all, they are important
friends.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]That's why I think 'understanding' is necessary. If you
truly care about and value them, I think you
should first understand how they came to accept
me.
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]...? How did that happen...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Well, it's simple... You should test whether you
yourself can accept me or not.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]If... you are able to reject me, then you will be in
the right. At that time, I will end my
relationship with the three of them and take on
the appropriate responsibility.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]On the contrary, if it were to happen that Neon-chan
accepts me, then those doubts would be cleared and
Neon-chan would also feel relieved, right?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F](Test whether I can accept it? What are you talking
about...)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Huh? Haven't you caught on? Well then, let me put it
in a way that suits us.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]It's the final lesson, Minato-chan♪ This is your one-
time 'first time' challenge to prove your
righteousness... Will you accept it?
\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Hehehe♪

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F](So that's what it is... Whether I will cross that
final line or not...)

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]I didn't think to reject that proposal strangely.
Maybe it's because the situation was looking
bad... but I thought it would be much easier to
understand than continuing to argue back and
forth.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F](It might be a big concern for the three of them...
but... I just can't see that kind of relationship
as normal...)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Of course... it's fine if you run away from the
competition because you can't match my cuteness,
you know? No one will complain, and it's not a
competition that is done just to understand our
comrades, right?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]...I'll accept it, don't underestimate me. The words to
withdraw from the three of them... never forget
them.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Nfufu, that's right, just like Minato-chan♪ Well then,
I'll go ahead to the bedroom, okay?♪
A
